casebody.data:
OAK KNOLL VILLAGE CONDOMINIUM OWNERS ASSOCIATION, INC., Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Chris Ann JAYE, Defendant-Movant. M-939/940 Sept. Term 2018
082210 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motions of Chris Ann Jaye for summary action (M-939) and for "immediate return of all funds extorted by void rulings via the NJ Supreme Court Rules" (M-940) are denied.
